data.description: Welcome Home!!! Discover the ultimate cozy and stylish living in the heart of Virginia Beach. One owner and meticulously maintained two-bedroom, two-bath unit. New carpet throughout. The open-floor layout seamlessly connects the dining room, kitchen and living room, great for entertaining guests or simply enjoying everyday life. Enjoy the convenience of an in-unit laundry room. Condo fees cover water, trash, sewer, community pool, clubhouse and beautiful ground maintenance. This home is near restaurants, shopping, schools, entertainment and military bases (Naval Station Norfolk, JEB Little Creek, Fort Story). Don't miss out - Schedule your showing today
